Title: Jackson Really Needs a Job
Overview:
Dear whomever Jackson happens to be seeking employment with at this time please accomodate his wishes and offer him a position within your establishment.

Letter Body: Give Jackson a job please. He's a really cool guy or whatever but's he's being a total fuckin' mooch and it is totally not crescent fresh.
